<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She returned to morning television on Tuesday following her summer break.</p>

<p>And after delighting fans with her TV return, Holly Willoughby was seen picking up some essentials at her local Marks &amp; Spencer in London on Wednesday.</p>

<p>The This Morning presenter, 39, cut a casual figure as she stepped out following her appearance on the ITV mainstay, wearing a khaki military style jacket.</p>

<p>Stepping out: Holly Willoughby was seen picking up some essentials at her local Marks &amp; Spencer in London on Wednesday</p>

<p>Holly styled her ensemble with a pair of form-fitting gym leggings which highlighted her toned legs, as well as a pair of tonal grey Nike trainers.</p>

<p>She layered her look with a simple grey jumper and carried her belongings in a chic black leather handbag.</p>

<p>The mother-of-three wore her signature blonde locks in a loose bouncy style, while highlighting her pretty features with soft touches of make-up. </p>

